package framework

    Description
    Deserializer
    Deserializer deserializes object or list of objects.
    JsonFilter
    JsonFilter represents class which can filter JSON objects without serializing them.
    JsonReader
    JsonReader reads from JSON file json object to deserialize it further.
    JsonWriter
    JsonWriter writes to JSON file json object.
    Operator
    Operator is enum of all available operation for JSON filter.
    Serializer
    Serializer serializes object or list of objects.
